title: 7 AM Hour - There's No Way Your Kid Said This!
description:
Happy Tuesday! Dave is still in Boston (He's back Thursday!) Falen is gearing up for her Spain Trip that she leaves for tomorrow & don't forget it's Prince's Birthday!

We announce our iHeartRadio Music Festival lineup, How to behave at a Gay Wedding, Talkback Tuesday: Funny things yoru kid/students said to you, Group Therapy, & More!
